<string id="yan_find_scientist_task_name">
	<text>Help Kruglov Take Measurements</text>
</string>
<string id="yan_find_scientist_task_text">
	<text>To approach X-16, strong psi-protection is required. The scientists are working on a prototype, but it needs calibration. Kruglov will handle the measurements, and my job, as always, is to protect him.</text>
</string>

<string id="yan_find_scientist_semenov_task_name">
	<text>Help Semenov Take Measurements</text>
</string>
<string id="yan_find_scientist_semenov_task_text">
	<text>To approach X-16, strong psi-protection is required. The scientists are working on a prototype, but it needs calibration. Semenov will take the measurements. I need to cover him.</text>
</string>

<string id="yan_find_vasilyev_task_name">
	<text>Find Vasilyev</text>
</string>
<string id="yan_find_vasilyev_task_text">
	<text>Vasilyev had precise information about the location of the entrance to Lab X-16. Sakharov suspects Vasilyev is dead. His signal was last coming from the swamps.</text>
</string>

<string id="yan_find_ghost_task_name">
	<text>Retrieve the Documents from Ghost</text>
</string>
<string id="yan_find_ghost_task_text">
	<text>I managed to shut down the installation. Vasilyev’s records say he and Ghost found the documents. Vasilyev didn’t have them, so they must still be with Ghost—who most likely didn’t survive.</text>
</string>

<string id="yan_provodnik_task_name">
	<text>Meet the Guide in the Cordon</text>
</string>
<string id="yan_provodnik_task_text">
	<text>It seems Ghost intended to send someone to meet with the Doctor via the Guide. I should meet the Guide in the ruined hamlet near the railway embankment.</text>
</string>

<string id="yan_kill_brain_task_1_name">
	<text>Escape the Lab</text>
</string>
<string id="yan_kill_brain_task_1_text">
	<text>I’ve dealt with the installation and recovered the documents. Now I just need to escape the lab without dying.</text>
</string>

<string id="yan_kill_brain_task_2_name">
	<text>Talk to Sakharov</text>
</string>
<string id="yan_kill_brain_task_2_text">
	<text>I barely made it out of the tunnels when Professor Sakharov requested a word with me.</text>
</string>


